Perfect location
central to all the main sights yet quiet enough to ensure a good nights sleep which is essential after all the sightseeing and walking
We had a family room which was ideal for a family including 2 teenagers
The hotel staff were friendly and helpful at all times
Our package included buffet breakfast which set us up for the day
Good facilities including gym (if you have enough energy after all the walking
free internet access and enough information to help you get around this amazing city
